WEBVTT

00:00.640 --> 00:02.800
<font color="white">I owe you both an apology.</font>

00:02.800 --> 00:06.280
<font color="yellow">'There were no Major Ryan Wilsons</font>
<font color="yellow">serving in Afghanistan</font>

00:06.280 --> 00:08.520
<font color="yellow">'at the time Ryan says he was there.</font>

00:08.520 --> 00:10.000
<font color="yellow">'It's a complete lie.'</font>

00:10.000 --> 00:13.600
<font color="white">Craig, someone painted the word</font>
<font color="white">"killer" on the deck of my boat.</font>

00:17.520 --> 00:20.160
<font color="white">Come near me or my daughter again</font>

00:20.160 --> 00:22.360
<font color="white">and there will be</font>
<font color="white">serious consequences.</font>

00:22.360 --> 00:24.600
<font color="cyan">Ryan's medal seems to be missing.</font>

00:24.600 --> 00:26.760
<font color="yellow">Ed.</font>

00:26.760 --> 00:28.440
<font color="yellow">I knew it was you.</font>

01:22.080 --> 01:23.400
<font color="white">I...</font>

01:23.400 --> 01:25.160
<font color="white">..have no excuse. I...</font>

01:26.240 --> 01:30.480
<font color="white">..picked it up, you came, and I</font>
<font color="white">put it in my pocket, and then, eh...</font>

01:30.480 --> 01:32.360
<font color="white">Er...</font>

01:32.360 --> 01:35.120
<font color="white">That was stupid. I...</font>

01:35.120 --> 01:36.520
<font color="white">I'm sorry.</font>

01:40.120 --> 01:42.840
<font color="yellow">My passport.</font>
<font color="white">Oh, yes. Um...</font>

01:42.840 --> 01:43.920
<font color="white">Well, I just...</font>

01:43.920 --> 01:45.640
<font color="yellow">You still don't trust me, do you?</font>

01:48.000 --> 01:49.120
<font color="white">Well, I...</font>

01:50.440 --> 01:54.680
<font color="white">Well, you love Abbie, I know that,</font>
<font color="white">and I know that she loves you.</font>

01:54.680 --> 01:57.760
<font color="yellow">What do I have to do to make</font>
<font color="yellow">you change your mind about me?</font>

01:57.760 --> 01:59.640
<font color="yellow">How do I prove...?</font>
<font color="white">It's not...</font>

02:00.840 --> 02:02.440
<font color="white">It's not about you.</font>

02:02.440 --> 02:03.480
<font color="white">It's...</font>

02:05.120 --> 02:07.400
<font color="white">It's about me. I...</font>

02:09.199 --> 02:13.280
<font color="white">Claire will tell you that I've been</font>
<font color="white">like this ever since Josh died,</font>

02:13.280 --> 02:14.440
<font color="white">so...</font>

02:17.080 --> 02:18.720
<font color="white">And...</font>

02:20.920 --> 02:25.720
<font color="white">..I would appreciate it</font>
<font color="white">if you didn't tell Claire or Abbie</font>

02:25.720 --> 02:27.040
<font color="white">about the medal.</font>

02:29.680 --> 02:31.880
<font color="white">RYAN SIGHS</font>
<font color="yellow">Come with me.</font>

02:41.440 --> 02:44.600
<font color="yellow">A very simple off-the-shelf</font>
<font color="yellow">tracking device.</font>

02:46.480 --> 02:49.400
<font color="yellow">I found it in Abbie's car.</font>

02:49.400 --> 02:50.560
<font color="white">Really?</font>

02:52.240 --> 02:53.600
<font color="yellow">I think I know who put it there.</font>

03:00.440 --> 03:01.800
<font color="white">George.</font>

03:03.480 --> 03:06.040
<font color="yellow">He seems to have found</font>
<font color="yellow">where we live.</font>

03:06.040 --> 03:09.000
<font color="yellow">I think we should keep this</font>
<font color="yellow">between me and you, yeah?</font>

03:09.000 --> 03:12.800
<font color="yellow">Abbie would freak if she realised</font>
<font color="yellow">that he was stalking her like this.</font>

03:12.800 --> 03:15.720
<font color="yellow">He's clearly struggling</font>
<font color="yellow">to let her go.</font>

03:15.720 --> 03:17.880
<font color="yellow">And who can blame him?</font>

03:25.680 --> 03:27.640
<font color="white">Oh, my phone.</font>
<font color="yellow">Hm?</font>

03:27.640 --> 03:28.880
<font color="white">I left it in your car.</font>

03:30.880 --> 03:32.760
<font color="white">Oh, damn.</font>

03:32.760 --> 03:34.280
<font color="white">I'm meant to be meeting Claire.</font>

03:34.280 --> 03:36.560
<font color="yellow">Take my car.</font>
<font color="white">No, it's too bloody late!</font>

03:39.000 --> 03:42.320
<font color="yellow">I wasn't going to show you this</font>
<font color="yellow">because I didn't know what it meant,</font>

03:42.320 --> 03:44.720
<font color="yellow">but I think George</font>
<font color="yellow">posted it through our letterbox.</font>

03:44.720 --> 03:47.720
<font color="yellow">That's why I was asking you</font>
<font color="yellow">about your time in the Navy.</font>

03:47.720 --> 03:49.400
<font color="yellow">He's making us all paranoid.</font>

03:50.800 --> 03:53.120
<font color="white">He's not going to stop</font>
<font color="white">until he's destroyed me,</font>

03:53.120 --> 03:55.160
<font color="white">my boat, my family.</font>

03:55.160 --> 03:57.360
<font color="yellow">Ed, look...</font>
<font color="white">No, it's...</font>

03:57.360 --> 04:00.880
<font color="white">You look after Abbie</font>
<font color="white">and I'll take care of George.</font>

04:22.280 --> 04:23.440
<font color="white">George!</font>

04:25.480 --> 04:27.640
<font color="white">HORN BEEPS</font>

04:29.760 --> 04:31.160
<font color="white">George!</font>

05:00.240 --> 05:02.040
<font color="white">FROM INSIDE: </font><font color="cyan">It's true!</font>

05:02.040 --> 05:04.800
<font color="cyan">Oh, shaved legs, the lot!</font>

05:04.800 --> 05:06.120
<font color="cyan">If you're a fine-looking woman,</font>

05:06.120 --> 05:09.920
<font color="cyan">a man goes crazy after a few months</font>
<font color="cyan">at sea. Believe me!</font>

05:09.920 --> 05:12.240
<font color="lime">Oh, here he comes,</font>
<font color="lime">Mata Hari himself.</font>

05:14.040 --> 05:16.080
<font color="white">Craig.</font>

05:16.080 --> 05:20.440
<font color="cyan">I were just saying</font>
<font color="cyan">one of our old mates passed on.</font>

05:20.440 --> 05:23.360
<font color="cyan">Oh, your name came up</font>
<font color="cyan">and... in the area, so...</font>

05:24.800 --> 05:27.560
<font color="white">Let's get a beer.</font>
<font color="cyan">Yeah, nice.</font>

05:27.560 --> 05:29.520
<font color="cyan">See you in a bit.</font>
<font color="lime">OK, thanks very much.</font>

05:29.520 --> 05:31.320
<font color="lime">Can I have a gin and tonic, please.</font>

05:31.320 --> 05:32.720
<font color="yellow">Mum, it's too early for that.</font>

05:32.720 --> 05:35.280
<font color="lime">It's never too early</font>
<font color="lime">for a G&T, Claire. </font><font color="yellow">True.</font>

05:44.920 --> 05:46.480
<font color="cyan">What are you playing at, Collier?</font>

05:46.480 --> 05:47.520
<font color="white">Me?</font>

05:49.520 --> 05:51.120
<font color="cyan">As I remember it...</font>

05:54.800 --> 05:57.320
<font color="cyan">..this photo was taken</font>
<font color="cyan">with your camera.</font>

05:59.040 --> 06:00.800
<font color="white">I didn't have a camera.</font>

06:00.800 --> 06:02.560
<font color="cyan">We all got one in Gibraltar.</font>

06:02.560 --> 06:04.160
<font color="white">Well, you may have done.</font>
<font color="white">I was skint.</font>

06:06.760 --> 06:08.480
<font color="white">HE EXHALES</font>

06:08.480 --> 06:10.640
<font color="cyan">So, Des is dead,</font>

06:10.640 --> 06:12.040
<font color="cyan">Arthur's still missing.</font>

06:13.360 --> 06:14.520
<font color="cyan">Who else can it be?</font>

06:15.480 --> 06:17.680
<font color="white">Well, it's not me,</font>
<font color="white">if that's what you're getting at.</font>

06:17.680 --> 06:19.880
<font color="white">Why would I want all this</font>
<font color="white">to come out now?</font>

06:19.880 --> 06:21.200
<font color="cyan">Then who's doing it?</font>

06:21.200 --> 06:23.760
<font color="white">It's just some local lad</font>
<font color="white">winding me up.</font>

06:26.280 --> 06:28.120
<font color="cyan">Look,</font>

06:28.120 --> 06:29.600
<font color="cyan">what happened with Baxter...</font>

06:29.600 --> 06:33.840
<font color="white">You... You make it sound like it was</font>
<font color="white">some sort of unfortunate accident.</font>

06:38.520 --> 06:40.480
<font color="cyan">What's in the past...</font>

06:42.320 --> 06:44.240
<font color="cyan">..stays in the past.</font>

06:54.880 --> 06:56.600
<font color="white">HE SIGHS</font>

06:59.880 --> 07:02.840
<font color="white">INDISTINCT</font>

07:02.840 --> 07:04.680
<font color="white">LAUGHTER,</font>
<font color="white">CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS</font>

07:16.440 --> 07:17.920
<font color="cyan">Hey!</font>

07:19.840 --> 07:21.360
<font color="yellow">How's work?</font>

07:21.360 --> 07:23.360
<font color="cyan">Urgh, you know, the usual.</font>

07:23.360 --> 07:25.360
<font color="cyan">I see you've taken your bandage off.</font>

07:25.360 --> 07:26.840
<font color="yellow">Mm-hm.</font>

07:28.000 --> 07:29.080
<font color="cyan">Ryan?</font>

07:31.840 --> 07:35.800
<font color="yellow">When I got home, your dad was here -</font>
<font color="yellow">inside the house.</font>

07:35.800 --> 07:38.200
<font color="yellow">Returning this.</font>

07:39.400 --> 07:40.960
<font color="cyan">My DAD took it?</font>

07:42.600 --> 07:44.600
<font color="yellow">I promised I wouldn't say anything.</font>

07:45.800 --> 07:48.040
<font color="yellow">I'm starting to worry about him.</font>

07:48.040 --> 07:49.720
<font color="yellow">You living with me,</font>

07:49.720 --> 07:52.080
<font color="yellow">he's still struggling with Josh,</font>
<font color="yellow">his work.</font>

07:54.200 --> 07:55.640
<font color="yellow">And now this.</font>

07:59.640 --> 08:01.560
<font color="cyan">That's my dad.</font>

08:01.560 --> 08:02.880
<font color="yellow">Turn it over.</font>

08:12.800 --> 08:14.800
<font color="white">Let me tell you why I didn't</font>
<font color="white">come to counselling.</font>

08:14.800 --> 08:17.040
<font color="yellow">Whatever it was,</font>
<font color="yellow">it was more important than me.</font>

08:17.040 --> 08:18.560
<font color="white">No!</font>

08:18.560 --> 08:21.080
<font color="yellow">If I mattered so much,</font>
<font color="yellow">you'd trust me with the truth.</font>

08:23.640 --> 08:25.520
<font color="yellow">What was Craig doing here?</font>

08:27.240 --> 08:28.960
<font color="white">When Des died,</font>

08:28.960 --> 08:31.720
<font color="white">I think it reminded him</font>
<font color="white">of how we all used to be.</font>

08:31.720 --> 08:34.200
<font color="white">SHE SCOFFS</font>

08:34.200 --> 08:37.919
<font color="yellow">You went to all those lengths</font>
<font color="yellow">to accuse Ryan of lying.</font>

08:37.919 --> 08:39.520
<font color="yellow">Look at you.</font>

08:39.520 --> 08:41.760
<font color="yellow">The sheer hypocrisy!</font>

09:02.120 --> 09:03.760
<font color="white">SHE GASPS</font>

09:03.760 --> 09:05.720
<font color="cyan">You've booked your flights?</font>

09:05.720 --> 09:08.320
<font color="lime">And I know for a fact that</font>
<font color="lime">that seat next to me is still empty.</font>

09:09.920 --> 09:13.280
<font color="lime">You know the reason you can't stand</font>
<font color="lime">your job... </font><font color="cyan">It doesn't matter.</font>

09:13.280 --> 09:14.640
<font color="cyan">I've quit.</font>

09:14.640 --> 09:16.160
<font color="lime">So what are you gonna do?</font>

09:16.160 --> 09:19.440
<font color="cyan">Ryan's gonna help me find</font>
<font color="cyan">something more suitable.</font>

09:19.440 --> 09:20.520
<font color="lime">Who for -</font>

09:20.520 --> 09:22.680
<font color="lime">you or him?</font>

09:22.680 --> 09:25.240
<font color="cyan">Why can't you just be supportive?</font>

09:25.240 --> 09:27.560
<font color="lime">I would be if I thought you was</font>
<font color="lime">doing the right thing but...</font>

09:27.560 --> 09:29.440
<font color="cyan">You're just jealous...</font>

09:29.440 --> 09:31.640
<font color="cyan">of me and Ryan.</font>

09:31.640 --> 09:34.120
<font color="cyan">You've always hated me giving</font>
<font color="cyan">my attention to anyone but you.</font>

09:35.400 --> 09:37.360
<font color="lime">You and I both know that's not true.</font>

09:38.480 --> 09:41.160
<font color="lime">And if you can't see that,</font>
<font color="lime">I give up.</font>

09:46.840 --> 09:49.640
<font color="white">SHIP'S HORN BLOWS</font>

09:49.640 --> 09:51.680
<font color="white">You seen my gutting knife?</font>

09:53.080 --> 09:54.400
<font color="yellow">What's the matter with you?</font>

09:56.400 --> 09:59.120
<font color="white">It's Claire, she's had enough.</font>
<font color="yellow">She said that?</font>

09:59.120 --> 10:01.600
<font color="white">You work all your life for something</font>
<font color="white">for you and your family,</font>

10:01.600 --> 10:02.680
<font color="white">and then some bastard...</font>

10:02.680 --> 10:04.520
<font color="yellow">Come on, mate, let's get to work.</font>

10:04.520 --> 10:06.760
<font color="yellow">The tide's turning, so let's go.</font>

10:22.960 --> 10:25.200
<font color="cyan">Mum, I don't have time for this.</font>

10:25.200 --> 10:28.080
<font color="lime">Well, look, it's my house,</font>
<font color="lime">so just stop shouting at me.</font>

10:28.080 --> 10:29.400
<font color="cyan">I'm not shouting!</font>

10:29.400 --> 10:31.440
<font color="lime">All you do these days</font>
<font color="lime">is shout at me.</font>

10:31.440 --> 10:33.440
<font color="cyan">You need to get dressed,</font>
<font color="cyan">for Christ's sake.</font>

10:33.440 --> 10:34.560
<font color="white">RYAN: </font><font color="yellow">Hello?</font>

10:34.560 --> 10:36.520
<font color="lime">Oh.</font>
<font color="yellow">Sorry, the door was open.</font>

10:36.520 --> 10:38.920
<font color="lime">Who are you?</font>
<font color="lime">Why are you always here?</font>

10:38.920 --> 10:40.760
<font color="cyan">Mum!</font>
<font color="lime">Just go away!</font>

10:40.760 --> 10:42.600
<font color="cyan">Mum!</font>
<font color="yellow">I'm Abbie's boyfriend.</font>

10:42.600 --> 10:45.280
<font color="cyan">It's not always like this. I'm...</font>

10:45.280 --> 10:48.240
<font color="cyan">I'm just a bit tired. </font><font color="yellow">I could</font>
<font color="yellow">watch her for a bit, if you like.</font>

10:48.240 --> 10:49.720
<font color="cyan">No, no, I'm fine.</font>

10:49.720 --> 10:51.040
<font color="yellow">Get some time for yourself.</font>

10:51.040 --> 10:53.640
<font color="yellow">Abbie says you like swimming,</font>
<font color="yellow">you know, to escape.</font>

10:53.640 --> 10:55.840
<font color="cyan">I don't know.</font>
<font color="cyan">As you can see, she's...</font>

10:55.840 --> 10:58.000
<font color="lime">I'm so sorry. Excuse me.</font>

10:58.000 --> 11:00.640
<font color="lime">My brain just goes off a little</font>
<font color="lime">from time to time.</font>

11:00.640 --> 11:03.080
<font color="lime">And I know exactly who you are -</font>
<font color="lime">you're Ryan.</font>

11:03.080 --> 11:05.280
<font color="lime">Hello.</font>
<font color="yellow">Hi.</font>

11:05.280 --> 11:07.960
<font color="yellow">You know, I can't promise much,</font>
<font color="yellow">but I know you like a game of cards.</font>

11:07.960 --> 11:10.680
<font color="lime">Oh, I do!</font>
<font color="yellow">I'm not doing anything else.</font>

11:10.680 --> 11:12.040
<font color="lime">Oh, right, let's go, then.</font>

11:12.040 --> 11:13.880
<font color="lime">Thanks very much.</font>

11:13.880 --> 11:16.560
<font color="lime">And, by the way,</font>
<font color="lime">you're a gorgeous-looking lad.</font>

11:16.560 --> 11:18.160
<font color="lime">Come on.</font>

11:18.160 --> 11:22.040
<font color="cyan">That's very kind of you, Ryan.</font>
<font color="cyan">Thank you.</font>

11:22.040 --> 11:24.400
<font color="yellow">No worries. It's all right.</font>

11:26.560 --> 11:29.160
<font color="white">Sorry I missed your call earlier.</font>
<font color="white">I was out on the boat.</font>

11:29.160 --> 11:32.320
<font color="yellow">'Did you know Craig Passarello</font>
<font color="yellow">served 18 months for GBH?'</font>

11:32.320 --> 11:34.200
<font color="white">Well, that doesn't surprise me.</font>

11:34.200 --> 11:36.480
<font color="yellow">There's not much else so far,</font>
<font color="yellow">I'm afraid.</font>

11:36.480 --> 11:38.200
<font color="yellow">'Perhaps if you told me</font>
<font color="yellow">a little more</font>

11:38.200 --> 11:40.400
<font color="yellow">'about what connects you</font>
<font color="yellow">to these men, then maybe...'</font>

11:40.400 --> 11:42.840
<font color="white">No, you know,</font>
<font color="white">it could be someone else.</font>

11:42.840 --> 11:45.000
<font color="white">A local lad - George Fitzgerald.</font>

11:45.000 --> 11:46.960
<font color="yellow">And this man knows about</font>
<font color="yellow">your time in the Navy?</font>

11:46.960 --> 11:48.760
<font color="white">Well, he knows I served, yeah.</font>

11:54.640 --> 11:56.200
<font color="lime">Who are you?</font>

12:10.806 --> 12:12.246
<font color="yellow">Ah.</font>

12:16.566 --> 12:18.606
<font color="cyan">Thar she blows!</font>

12:18.606 --> 12:19.846
<font color="yellow">You calling me a whale?</font>

12:19.846 --> 12:21.846
<font color="cyan">Not on porpoise.</font>
<font color="white">CLAIRE CHUCKLES</font>

12:21.846 --> 12:24.126
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

12:24.126 --> 12:25.646
<font color="cyan">Oh, I just...</font>

12:25.646 --> 12:28.446
<font color="cyan">You said if I had</font>
<font color="cyan">any concerns about Ed.</font>

12:28.446 --> 12:30.246
<font color="yellow">What's happened now?</font>

12:31.966 --> 12:34.806
<font color="cyan">Has he told you about the photo</font>
<font color="cyan">that was sent to him on the boat -</font>

12:34.806 --> 12:36.806
<font color="cyan">him and his mates in the Navy?</font>

12:36.806 --> 12:38.806
<font color="yellow">Not more bloody secrets!</font>

12:38.806 --> 12:40.446
<font color="yellow">Why can't he just talk to me?</font>

12:41.686 --> 12:43.366
<font color="yellow">I even asked him last night.</font>

12:43.366 --> 12:46.766
<font color="yellow">One of his old friends turned up</font>
<font color="yellow">out of the blue.</font>

12:47.886 --> 12:49.526
<font color="yellow">What's going on, Bob?</font>

12:49.526 --> 12:50.966
<font color="cyan">I'm no clearer, I don't know.</font>

12:52.366 --> 12:54.566
<font color="cyan">I'm just really worried about him,</font>
<font color="cyan">that's all.</font>

12:54.566 --> 12:56.886
<font color="white">SHE SIGHS</font>

12:56.886 --> 12:57.966
<font color="yellow">Come here.</font>

12:59.086 --> 13:00.526
<font color="white">SHE SIGHS</font>

13:08.766 --> 13:10.286
<font color="white">HE SIGHS</font>

13:17.166 --> 13:18.766
<font color="yellow">You said you weren't going.</font>

13:20.126 --> 13:21.686
<font color="white">I know, but, um...</font>

13:22.886 --> 13:25.926
<font color="white">Well, I liked Des -</font>
<font color="white">he made me laugh.</font>

13:25.926 --> 13:27.406
<font color="white">Just paying my respects.</font>

13:28.886 --> 13:31.606
<font color="yellow">You didn't see him</font>
<font color="yellow">for near 30 years.</font>

13:31.606 --> 13:33.126
<font color="white">PHYLLIS: </font><font color="lime">Claire?</font>

13:33.126 --> 13:34.726
<font color="lime">Claire, where are you?</font>

13:34.726 --> 13:36.166
<font color="yellow">I'm up here.</font>

13:36.166 --> 13:37.766
<font color="yellow">You'll have to wait.</font>

13:41.246 --> 13:43.406
<font color="yellow">I was going to go out.</font>

13:43.406 --> 13:45.646
<font color="yellow">I assumed you'd be here with Mum.</font>

13:45.646 --> 13:48.646
<font color="white">Oh, I-I'm sorry.</font>
<font color="white">I didn't know. Um...</font>

13:49.966 --> 13:51.486
<font color="white">Can you call Abbie?</font>

13:51.486 --> 13:53.926
<font color="yellow">Abbie's not picking up.</font>

13:53.926 --> 13:55.646
<font color="yellow">My brother's on holiday.</font>

13:57.086 --> 13:58.606
<font color="yellow">Any other suggestions?</font>

14:02.606 --> 14:05.086
<font color="yellow">I was going to look at a care home.</font>

14:12.926 --> 14:14.006
<font color="white">Are you sure?</font>

14:15.406 --> 14:16.686
<font color="yellow">I...</font>

14:17.766 --> 14:19.766
<font color="yellow">..can't do this any more.</font>

14:19.766 --> 14:22.886
<font color="white">You're doing an amazing job, Claire.</font>

14:22.886 --> 14:25.166
<font color="yellow">No. No, I'm not.</font>

14:26.286 --> 14:27.406
<font color="yellow">Neither of us are.</font>

14:29.526 --> 14:31.086
<font color="white">Well...</font>

14:31.086 --> 14:33.526
<font color="white">I just don't know how we're</font>
<font color="white">going to afford it, that's all.</font>

14:43.846 --> 14:46.606
<font color="yellow">You bought that for Josh's funeral.</font>

14:52.006 --> 14:53.606
<font color="white">I wish I'd spoken...</font>

14:56.566 --> 14:57.926
<font color="white">..at the church.</font>

15:01.046 --> 15:02.886
<font color="yellow">Neither of us could.</font>

15:05.086 --> 15:06.446
<font color="yellow">Bob did us proud.</font>

15:06.446 --> 15:07.646
<font color="white">And Abbie.</font>

15:07.646 --> 15:09.566
<font color="white">SOFTLY: </font><font color="yellow">And Abbie.</font>

15:11.566 --> 15:13.206
<font color="white">I still see him, you know.</font>

15:16.646 --> 15:18.126
<font color="white">Talk to him.</font>

15:46.566 --> 15:48.446
<font color="white">HE TAPS</font>

15:48.446 --> 15:49.606
<font color="white">George?</font>

17:17.685 --> 17:18.965
<font color="cyan">Mum?</font>

17:20.046 --> 17:21.406
<font color="yellow">Hi, love.</font>

17:22.566 --> 17:24.246
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

17:24.246 --> 17:26.126
<font color="cyan">I just came to see how you all were.</font>

17:32.806 --> 17:34.286
<font color="cyan">You putting Nan in a home?</font>

17:34.286 --> 17:35.926
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

17:35.926 --> 17:37.446
<font color="yellow">I just...</font>

17:37.446 --> 17:38.926
<font color="yellow">I don't know.</font>

17:40.126 --> 17:41.526
<font color="yellow">The dementia care is amazing...</font>

17:41.526 --> 17:42.886
<font color="cyan">If it was you, I'd do it.</font>

17:45.246 --> 17:46.926
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

17:48.006 --> 17:51.046
<font color="cyan">If it meant the best care for you,</font>
<font color="cyan">then yeah.</font>

17:55.286 --> 17:57.606
<font color="cyan">But I know you're only doing it</font>
<font color="cyan">cos I'm not here.</font>

17:58.926 --> 18:01.566
<font color="yellow">None of this is your fault.</font>

18:01.566 --> 18:03.726
<font color="yellow">Besides, we can't afford it anyway.</font>

18:03.726 --> 18:05.926
<font color="yellow">The council might</font>
<font color="yellow">give us half, but...</font>

18:05.926 --> 18:07.886
<font color="cyan">Ryan was talking about how</font>
<font color="cyan">we might be able to help.</font>

18:07.886 --> 18:09.486
<font color="yellow">No. No, no, no.</font>

18:09.486 --> 18:11.766
<font color="cyan">I know Dad would never</font>
<font color="cyan">accept a handout,</font>

18:11.766 --> 18:13.966
<font color="cyan">but Ryan thought</font>
<font color="cyan">you could get a loan</font>

18:13.966 --> 18:15.446
<font color="cyan">against the value of the house.</font>

18:17.726 --> 18:19.646
<font color="yellow">I'll speak to your dad.</font>

18:25.406 --> 18:26.686
<font color="yellow">Abbie...</font>

18:28.646 --> 18:30.286
<font color="cyan">I need to tell you something...</font>

18:32.406 --> 18:33.646
<font color="cyan">..about Dad.</font>

18:36.526 --> 18:38.766
<font color="white">DOORBELL RINGS</font>

18:42.366 --> 18:44.566
<font color="white">Uh, yeah, I'm just going</font>
<font color="white">to a funeral.</font>

18:45.686 --> 18:48.046
<font color="white">I think this might be a password</font>
<font color="white">for that tracking device</font>

18:48.046 --> 18:51.006
<font color="white">that you found under Abbie's car.</font>

18:51.006 --> 18:53.966
<font color="white">Don't we need to find out how long</font>
<font color="white">he's been tracking her?</font>

18:53.966 --> 18:55.806
<font color="yellow">Yeah, come in.</font>

18:58.846 --> 19:03.406
<font color="yellow">According to this, George started</font>
<font color="yellow">tracking Abbie four days ago.</font>

19:03.406 --> 19:06.046
<font color="white">Well, he told me</font>
<font color="white">he was tracking you.</font>

19:06.046 --> 19:10.726
<font color="white">That you'd gone to Cerrick Point</font>
<font color="white">at three in the morning.</font>

19:10.726 --> 19:13.206
<font color="yellow">That's odd.</font>
<font color="white">What's that?</font>

19:13.206 --> 19:17.446
<font color="yellow">Two days ago, it says</font>
<font color="yellow">that Abbie travelled 23 miles.</font>

19:18.446 --> 19:20.046
<font color="yellow">I thought she was at work.</font>

19:21.166 --> 19:22.686
<font color="white">Oh, no, well...</font>

19:22.686 --> 19:24.926
<font color="white">..that's where I went.</font>

19:26.006 --> 19:27.686
<font color="white">To see a friend.</font>

19:29.446 --> 19:31.086
<font color="white">Why would she follow me?</font>

19:32.926 --> 19:34.646
<font color="yellow">She wouldn't.</font>

19:40.326 --> 19:43.686
<font color="yellow">Yep. Yep, it's here.</font>

19:43.686 --> 19:45.126
<font color="white">HE SIGHS</font>

19:45.126 --> 19:46.886
<font color="white">He's been tracking me as well.</font>

19:49.566 --> 19:51.486
<font color="white">This is all my fault.</font>

19:51.486 --> 19:54.606
<font color="white">When we first met</font>
<font color="white">I didn't know anything about you,</font>

19:54.606 --> 19:57.566
<font color="white">and George said that he could</font>
<font color="white">find out some things.</font>

19:57.566 --> 19:58.886
<font color="yellow">About me?</font>

19:58.886 --> 20:01.086
<font color="white">Yeah. But he just must</font>
<font color="white">have made stuff up.</font>

20:02.366 --> 20:04.966
<font color="white">He got me to turn Abbie against you.</font>

20:04.966 --> 20:07.766
<font color="yellow">George just wants Abbie back.</font>
<font color="white">Don't defend him!</font>

20:07.766 --> 20:09.926
<font color="white">I've... I've gotta go.</font>

20:09.926 --> 20:12.686
<font color="white">Don't worry. I'll sort it.</font>

20:17.646 --> 20:20.126
<font color="white">CAR STARTS</font>

20:29.406 --> 20:31.046
<font color="white">CAR STARTS</font>

20:48.126 --> 20:50.446
<font color="white">HE SIGHS</font>

20:50.446 --> 20:52.446
<font color="cyan">You're too late.</font>

20:52.446 --> 20:53.966
<font color="cyan">It's over.</font>

20:55.206 --> 20:58.606
<font color="cyan">You asked me</font>
<font color="cyan">to investigate these men.</font>

20:58.606 --> 21:01.486
<font color="cyan">I was hoping one of them</font>
<font color="cyan">would show up.</font>

21:01.486 --> 21:03.206
<font color="cyan">Why did you?</font>

21:03.206 --> 21:05.046
<font color="white">Well, Des was a good friend of mine.</font>

21:05.046 --> 21:06.686
<font color="white">I can't believe I missed it.</font>

21:06.686 --> 21:10.606
<font color="white">Everything that I do at the moment</font>
<font color="white">seems to be...</font>

21:10.606 --> 21:11.926
<font color="white">Are you expecting someone?</font>

21:11.926 --> 21:13.446
<font color="cyan">I'm being followed.</font>

21:14.726 --> 21:16.086
<font color="white">Who by?</font>

21:18.726 --> 21:20.926
<font color="cyan">If you're serious about</font>
<font color="cyan">me finding out</font>

21:20.926 --> 21:22.526
<font color="cyan">who's sending you this photo,</font>

21:22.526 --> 21:26.486
<font color="cyan">you need to tell me more about</font>
<font color="cyan">your time on HMS Levenston.</font>

21:26.486 --> 21:28.366
<font color="cyan">When was the photo taken?</font>

21:28.366 --> 21:29.886
<font color="white">It was the early '90s, I guess.</font>

21:29.886 --> 21:32.726
<font color="cyan">Try 1994. Gibraltar.</font>

21:32.726 --> 21:35.886
<font color="cyan">Not long after you came back,</font>
<font color="cyan">all four of you left the Navy -</font>

21:35.886 --> 21:37.126
<font color="cyan">why was that?</font>

21:39.046 --> 21:41.206
<font color="cyan">An incident occurred in Gibraltar</font>

21:41.206 --> 21:43.926
<font color="cyan">that for some reason</font>
<font color="cyan">is still classified.</font>

21:43.926 --> 21:46.526
<font color="cyan">You were there -</font>
<font color="cyan">tell me what happened.</font>

21:46.526 --> 21:48.366
<font color="white">I can't.</font>

21:50.086 --> 21:51.686
<font color="cyan">What exactly are you hiding?</font>

21:56.806 --> 21:58.846
<font color="yellow">Yes, I wanted to ask about</font>

21:58.846 --> 22:02.126
<font color="yellow">getting a loan against</font>
<font color="yellow">the value of the house.</font>

22:02.126 --> 22:03.886
<font color="lime">'What's the name?'</font>
<font color="yellow">Claire Collier.</font>

22:03.886 --> 22:06.126
<font color="lime">'Wife of Ed Collier?'</font>
<font color="yellow">Yes, that's right.</font>

22:06.126 --> 22:08.326
<font color="lime">'Mr Collier already</font>
<font color="lime">took out a loan.'</font>

22:08.326 --> 22:10.886
<font color="yellow">Did he?</font>
<font color="lime">'Yeah.'</font>

22:10.886 --> 22:12.646
<font color="yellow">Well, when was that?</font>

22:12.646 --> 22:14.926
<font color="lime">'A couple of days ago.</font>
<font color="lime">He came by to get the money.'</font>

22:17.126 --> 22:18.406
<font color="lime">'Mrs Collier?'</font>

22:30.846 --> 22:32.286
<font color="yellow">What are you doing here?</font>

22:33.886 --> 22:35.206
<font color="cyan">Nice house.</font>

22:35.206 --> 22:37.686
<font color="yellow">I said, what are you doing here?</font>

22:39.246 --> 22:40.766
<font color="cyan">Where's Ed?</font>

22:40.766 --> 22:41.966
<font color="yellow">Out on the boat.</font>

22:41.966 --> 22:43.926
<font color="cyan">Oh, aye?</font>

22:43.926 --> 22:46.126
<font color="yellow">Why have you come back</font>
<font color="yellow">after all these years?</font>

22:46.126 --> 22:47.406
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

22:48.886 --> 22:50.486
<font color="cyan">You don't wanna know.</font>

22:50.486 --> 22:52.166
<font color="yellow">I'm calling the police.</font>

22:53.606 --> 22:55.166
<font color="cyan">I doubt that, love.</font>

23:01.406 --> 23:03.926
<font color="white">SEAGULLS SQUAWK</font>

23:08.406 --> 23:09.486
<font color="white">Abs?</font>

23:09.486 --> 23:11.086
<font color="white">What are you doing here?</font>

23:18.086 --> 23:20.246
<font color="cyan">I know you took Ryan's medal.</font>

23:20.246 --> 23:21.846
<font color="white">Well, I thought he was...</font>

23:21.846 --> 23:23.326
<font color="cyan">He's really concerned about you.</font>

23:24.326 --> 23:25.726
<font color="white">I've been to see him.</font>

23:26.766 --> 23:29.686
<font color="cyan">Why?</font>
<font color="white">We had a good talk,</font>

23:29.686 --> 23:33.086
<font color="white">and I realised that we both have</font>
<font color="white">your best interests at heart.</font>

23:33.086 --> 23:36.686
<font color="white">You said to give him a chance,</font>
<font color="white">and you were right.</font>

23:38.286 --> 23:39.646
<font color="white">As you usually are.</font>

23:48.206 --> 23:51.126
<font color="white">Does your mum know about the medal?</font>

23:51.126 --> 23:54.646
<font color="white">SHOUTING</font>
<font color="lime">James, come over here, see this!</font>

23:54.646 --> 23:55.686
<font color="yellow">Somebody help!</font>

23:57.366 --> 23:59.686
<font color="lime">There's somebody there.</font>

23:59.686 --> 24:01.926
<font color="yellow">Who's that?</font>
<font color="yellow">What's going on?</font>

24:01.926 --> 24:03.886
<font color="lime">Somebody call the police!</font>

24:03.886 --> 24:05.606
<font color="cyan">What's happened?</font>
<font color="white">No!</font>

24:05.606 --> 24:06.686
<font color="white">No. No, Abbie.</font>

24:08.326 --> 24:10.646
<font color="white">ABBIE GASPS</font>

24:40.011 --> 24:43.251
<font color="white">INDISTINCT CHATTER</font>

24:49.651 --> 24:51.291
<font color="cyan">What do you think happened?</font>

24:51.291 --> 24:53.531
<font color="white">Oh, I don't know.</font>

24:53.531 --> 24:54.851
<font color="white">I'm sure the police will...</font>

24:54.851 --> 24:55.931
<font color="cyan">This is just like Josh.</font>

24:57.971 --> 24:59.571
<font color="lime">Abs.</font>

24:59.571 --> 25:00.731
<font color="lime">Is it true?</font>

25:02.331 --> 25:04.251
<font color="lime">I'm so sorry.</font>

25:07.771 --> 25:09.451
<font color="yellow">Abbie.</font>

25:16.091 --> 25:18.411
<font color="lime">Ed, are you all right?</font>

25:18.411 --> 25:20.811
<font color="white">I'm fine, Katz. I'm fine.</font>

25:30.411 --> 25:32.571
<font color="yellow">Mr Collier.</font>

25:32.571 --> 25:34.091
<font color="yellow">Detective Inspector Nott.</font>

25:34.091 --> 25:36.451
<font color="yellow">I understand you were the one</font>
<font color="yellow">who called it in.</font>

25:36.451 --> 25:37.931
<font color="white">Yes, that's right, yeah.</font>

25:37.931 --> 25:39.651
<font color="yellow">What time did you find the body?</font>

25:39.651 --> 25:42.251
<font color="white">Oh, no, somebody else found him.</font>
<font color="white">I was by my boat.</font>

25:43.811 --> 25:46.371
<font color="white">Have you no idea how he...?</font>
<font color="yellow">Not yet.</font>

25:46.371 --> 25:47.931
<font color="yellow">Did you know the deceased?</font>

25:48.931 --> 25:51.531
<font color="white">George, yeah, yeah,</font>
<font color="white">he was a local lifeguard.</font>

25:53.731 --> 25:55.451
<font color="white">Nice lad.</font>

25:55.451 --> 25:57.731
<font color="yellow">Whatever the circumstances,</font>

25:57.731 --> 26:00.931
<font color="yellow">we need to get an idea</font>
<font color="yellow">of his last few days.</font>

26:00.931 --> 26:04.651
<font color="yellow">Don't go too far</font>
<font color="yellow">because I'll need to talk to you.</font>

26:15.011 --> 26:17.171
<font color="yellow">You broke into his campervan?</font>

26:17.171 --> 26:18.571
<font color="white">Well, George was spying on me.</font>

26:18.571 --> 26:20.291
<font color="yellow">Spying on you?</font>

26:20.291 --> 26:22.531
<font color="white">I think he found this photo of me</font>
<font color="white">and for some reason</font>

26:22.531 --> 26:24.331
<font color="white">he just sent it to everyone.</font>

26:26.371 --> 26:28.211
<font color="yellow">What does it mean?</font>

26:28.211 --> 26:30.131
<font color="white">I think George</font>
<font color="white">is just winding me up.</font>

26:30.131 --> 26:31.931
<font color="yellow">Well, if you don't know</font>
<font color="yellow">what it means,</font>

26:31.931 --> 26:34.411
<font color="yellow">how can you be wound up about it?</font>

26:34.411 --> 26:35.571
<font color="yellow">Ed...</font>

26:37.211 --> 26:39.171
<font color="yellow">..just tell me.</font>

26:52.131 --> 26:53.491
<font color="yellow">I called the bank...</font>

26:55.291 --> 26:56.731
<font color="yellow">..to borrow some money.</font>

26:56.731 --> 26:58.931
<font color="white">All right, now, I can explain.</font>
<font color="yellow">I'm sure you can, Ed.</font>

26:58.931 --> 27:00.331
<font color="white">This is just money I put aside...</font>

27:00.331 --> 27:03.371
<font color="yellow">You swore to me</font>
<font color="yellow">that you didn't take Ryan's medal.</font>

27:03.371 --> 27:05.811
<font color="white">Oh, now, that was just stupid.</font>
<font color="white">I needed to know whether he...</font>

27:05.811 --> 27:07.091
<font color="yellow">I don't care.</font>

27:07.091 --> 27:09.091
<font color="yellow">You're stealing money,</font>

27:09.091 --> 27:10.851
<font color="yellow">Ryan's medal,</font>

27:10.851 --> 27:14.011
<font color="yellow">you can't tell me the truth</font>
<font color="yellow">about this bloody photo.</font>

27:14.011 --> 27:15.971
<font color="white">I can tell you the truth,</font>
<font color="white">but I can't tell you...</font>

27:15.971 --> 27:17.171
<font color="yellow">I want you to go.</font>

27:20.291 --> 27:21.851
<font color="yellow">Get out.</font>

27:21.851 --> 27:22.931
<font color="yellow">Go!</font>

27:23.891 --> 27:24.931
<font color="yellow">Go.</font>

27:27.091 --> 27:29.491
<font color="white">SHE SOBS</font>

27:36.331 --> 27:38.691
<font color="cyan">I heard he jumped off Ratson Head.</font>
<font color="lime">Yeah.</font>

27:38.691 --> 27:41.051
<font color="yellow">He was stabbed - back of the neck.</font>

27:41.051 --> 27:43.771
<font color="yellow">Snapped his spine,</font>
<font color="yellow">according to the cops.</font>

27:43.771 --> 27:46.411
<font color="cyan">Have they spoken to your dad</font>
<font color="cyan">about it yet?</font>

27:46.411 --> 27:47.931
<font color="cyan">I heard him and George had a fight.</font>

27:47.931 --> 27:49.451
<font color="yellow">Give it a rest, eh?</font>

27:53.171 --> 27:54.691
<font color="yellow">I'm OK.</font>

27:56.211 --> 27:58.651
<font color="white">I'm just trying to help.</font>
<font color="yellow">I don't need you to help.</font>

27:58.651 --> 28:00.131
<font color="cyan">Abs.</font>

28:01.651 --> 28:03.331
<font color="yellow">Sorry. I'm OK.</font>

28:11.251 --> 28:14.131
<font color="yellow">Just say it. You usually do.</font>

28:14.131 --> 28:19.131
<font color="cyan">On the pub CCTV, there's images</font>
<font color="cyan">of Ed really laying into George.</font>

28:19.131 --> 28:20.451
<font color="yellow">When?</font>

28:20.451 --> 28:21.931
<font color="cyan">A couple of days ago.</font>

28:21.931 --> 28:24.851
<font color="cyan">And at one stage it looks like</font>
<font color="cyan">he's trying to run him over.</font>

28:24.851 --> 28:26.651
<font color="cyan">Well, what do I do with it?</font>

28:30.131 --> 28:33.451
<font color="white">SHIP'S HORN BLOWS</font>

28:42.691 --> 28:47.491
<font color="white">ECHOING: No!</font>

28:47.491 --> 28:49.651
<font color="white">HE GASPS</font>

29:02.451 --> 29:03.811
<font color="lime">Thanks.</font>

29:09.211 --> 29:10.411
<font color="cyan">Here you go.</font>

29:10.411 --> 29:11.691
<font color="yellow">I have to make myself clear.</font>

29:13.211 --> 29:15.411
<font color="yellow">If, in the course</font>
<font color="yellow">of my investigation,</font>

29:15.411 --> 29:18.771
<font color="yellow">I find anything that links you</font>
<font color="yellow">to George Fitzgerald's murder...</font>

29:18.771 --> 29:19.931
<font color="white">I didn't kill him!</font>

29:19.931 --> 29:23.091
<font color="yellow">..I will be obliged by law</font>
<font color="yellow">to pass that on to the police.</font>

29:23.091 --> 29:24.811
<font color="yellow">Am I making myself clear?</font>

29:29.371 --> 29:32.451
<font color="yellow">What does the name Nicholas Baxter</font>
<font color="yellow">mean to you?</font>

29:34.731 --> 29:37.291
<font color="yellow">A sublieutenant on HMS Levenston.</font>

29:37.291 --> 29:39.891
<font color="yellow">Found floating in</font>
<font color="yellow">the Gibraltar docks,</font>

29:39.891 --> 29:42.051
<font color="yellow">possibly drug-related.</font>

29:42.051 --> 29:44.531
<font color="yellow">Ring any bells?</font>

29:44.531 --> 29:46.731
<font color="white">I've gotta go.</font>
<font color="yellow">What are you running away from?</font>

29:50.771 --> 29:53.851
<font color="white">CAR DOOR OPENS, CLOSES</font>

29:53.851 --> 29:56.611
<font color="white">CAR STARTS</font>

30:21.451 --> 30:23.891
<font color="cyan">You told me you weren't</font>
<font color="cyan">going to Des's funeral.</font>

30:23.891 --> 30:26.091
<font color="white">Well, I changed my mind.</font>
<font color="white">How did you know I was here?</font>

30:26.091 --> 30:27.851
<font color="cyan">Who was that woman</font>
<font color="cyan">you were talking to?</font>

30:27.851 --> 30:30.931
<font color="white">What are you doing hanging around</font>
<font color="white">my house and upsetting my wife?</font>

30:30.931 --> 30:33.571
<font color="cyan">You were always</font>
<font color="cyan">the weakest fucking link.</font>

30:33.571 --> 30:36.291
<font color="white">If we hadn't all listened to you</font>
<font color="white">then we wouldn't be here, would we?</font>

30:36.291 --> 30:38.851
<font color="cyan">And if we all listened to you</font>
<font color="cyan">we'd probably be in fucking prison.</font>

30:38.851 --> 30:40.851
<font color="cyan">No wife, no family.</font>

30:42.051 --> 30:45.931
<font color="white">I know what I did</font>
<font color="white">and what I've had to hide.</font>

30:45.931 --> 30:47.891
<font color="white">But I'm not the only one, am I?</font>

30:48.891 --> 30:50.491
<font color="cyan">Des is dead.</font>

30:50.491 --> 30:52.091
<font color="cyan">I reckon Arthur's copped it.</font>

30:53.331 --> 30:54.931
<font color="cyan">That kid George is dead.</font>

30:56.491 --> 30:57.931
<font color="cyan">You might be next.</font>

31:12.931 --> 31:13.971
<font color="yellow">What you doing?</font>

31:15.651 --> 31:17.971
<font color="cyan">I was just going to unpack</font>
<font color="cyan">some of my stuff.</font>

31:17.971 --> 31:19.131
<font color="cyan">I know it's all junk, but...</font>

31:19.131 --> 31:22.891
<font color="yellow">It's not junk -</font>
<font color="yellow">it's you, it's who you are.</font>

31:24.651 --> 31:25.931
<font color="cyan">I shouldn't have left.</font>

31:28.091 --> 31:31.411
<font color="cyan">Mum and Dad, ever since Josh died,</font>
<font color="cyan">I've been holding them together.</font>

31:31.411 --> 31:33.811
<font color="cyan">And now that I've gone...</font>

31:37.451 --> 31:40.611
<font color="cyan">..I just feel like</font>
<font color="cyan">I'm losing everyone.</font>

31:40.611 --> 31:43.051
<font color="cyan">Mum, Dad, Katz.</font>

31:43.051 --> 31:44.131
<font color="yellow">You've got me.</font>

31:45.731 --> 31:48.731
<font color="cyan">But maybe moving in together</font>
<font color="cyan">so soon was a mistake.</font>

31:48.731 --> 31:50.731
<font color="yellow">It's not a mistake.</font>

31:52.371 --> 31:56.011
<font color="cyan">I want to be here with you.</font>
<font color="cyan">I really do.</font>

31:58.571 --> 32:02.171
<font color="cyan">But it just feels like everything</font>
<font color="cyan">I do at the moment is wrong.</font>

32:03.971 --> 32:05.971
<font color="yellow">Oh, come here.</font>

32:07.131 --> 32:08.771
<font color="yellow">You're being silly.</font>

32:08.771 --> 32:10.931
<font color="yellow">It's all right, yeah?</font>

32:12.171 --> 32:14.331
<font color="yellow">Oh.</font>

32:14.331 --> 32:15.771
<font color="yellow">It'll be all right. Hm?</font>

32:25.491 --> 32:28.331
<font color="lime">Ma'am.</font>
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

32:28.331 --> 32:30.171
<font color="yellow">Sorry for the delay.</font>

32:30.171 --> 32:31.411
<font color="yellow">And sorry about the smell -</font>

32:31.411 --> 32:33.651
<font color="yellow">it's the best we could do</font>
<font color="yellow">in the circumstances.</font>

32:33.651 --> 32:36.171
<font color="white">Ah, that's all right,</font>
<font color="white">I'm used to the smell of fish.</font>

32:36.171 --> 32:38.171
<font color="yellow">Oh.</font>
<font color="white">SHE CHUCKLES</font>

32:38.171 --> 32:40.371
<font color="yellow">Right. You were going</font>
<font color="yellow">to make a statement</font>

32:40.371 --> 32:43.411
<font color="yellow">concerning George Fitzgerald's</font>
<font color="yellow">murder - is that right?</font>

32:43.411 --> 32:45.571
<font color="white">Yeah, yeah, anything to help.</font>

32:45.571 --> 32:47.771
<font color="yellow">In which case, perhaps we can start</font>
<font color="yellow">with you telling me</font>

32:47.771 --> 32:51.011
<font color="yellow">what you were doing by</font>
<font color="yellow">his campervan yesterday afternoon.</font>

32:51.011 --> 32:52.531
<font color="white">Uh...</font>

32:52.531 --> 32:55.811
<font color="yellow">And be careful, Mr Collier,</font>
<font color="yellow">we've a witness who saw you there.</font>

32:55.811 --> 32:58.211
<font color="white">Oh, well, yeah, you know,</font>
<font color="white">I was there.</font>

32:58.211 --> 32:59.971
<font color="yellow">Because...?</font>

32:59.971 --> 33:02.131
<font color="white">I-I wanted to see him, talk to him.</font>

33:02.131 --> 33:04.651
<font color="yellow">What did you want to see him about?</font>

33:04.651 --> 33:06.931
<font color="white">Oh.</font>
<font color="white">HE CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY</font>

33:06.931 --> 33:09.211
<font color="white">Nothing specific.</font>
<font color="white">I-I wasn't even sure he was there.</font>

33:09.211 --> 33:13.291
<font color="white">I was just passing.</font>
<font color="white">I mean, I've known George for years.</font>

33:13.291 --> 33:15.451
<font color="yellow">Did you go inside the campervan?</font>

33:20.091 --> 33:22.251
<font color="white">Yeah. Yeah, I did.</font>

33:24.651 --> 33:26.451
<font color="yellow">Why would you go inside</font>
<font color="yellow">his campervan</font>

33:26.451 --> 33:28.291
<font color="yellow">if you knew he wasn't there?</font>

33:28.291 --> 33:30.891
<font color="white">Well, I mean, he might have been</font>
<font color="white">asleep. </font><font color="yellow">Well, was he asleep?</font>

33:30.891 --> 33:32.611
<font color="white">No. No, he wasn't asleep.</font>

33:32.611 --> 33:34.531
<font color="white">Yeah. Well, he wasn't there.</font>

33:36.771 --> 33:39.211
<font color="yellow">I hear your boat got sabotaged.</font>

33:40.971 --> 33:43.771
<font color="white">Yes.</font>
<font color="yellow">Who did you blame for that?</font>

33:43.771 --> 33:46.331
<font color="white">HE STAMMERS: I'm not sure.</font>

33:46.331 --> 33:47.971
<font color="yellow">George Fitzgerald?</font>
<font color="white">No, no.</font>

33:47.971 --> 33:50.451
<font color="white">But I...</font>
<font color="white">I-I did talk to him about that.</font>

33:50.451 --> 33:51.971
<font color="yellow">And what did he say?</font>

33:51.971 --> 33:54.451
<font color="white">Well, he denied it.</font>
<font color="white">I mean, of course he did.</font>

33:54.451 --> 33:56.491
<font color="yellow">Is that why you went to see him -</font>
<font color="yellow">to confront him?</font>

33:56.491 --> 33:58.171
<font color="white">No, no. I...</font>

33:58.171 --> 33:59.211
<font color="white">No, I believed him.</font>

34:01.731 --> 34:03.931
<font color="yellow">In that case, would you</font>
<font color="yellow">have any objection to us</font>

34:03.931 --> 34:06.691
<font color="yellow">having a sample of your DNA?</font>

34:06.691 --> 34:08.331
<font color="yellow">Or do I have to arrest you?</font>

34:10.091 --> 34:11.610
<font color="white">Arrest me - what for?</font>

34:11.610 --> 34:15.091
<font color="yellow">Well, I could start with</font>
<font color="yellow">breaking and entering.</font>

34:35.846 --> 34:37.766
<font color="yellow">Hey.</font>
<font color="cyan">Hey.</font>

34:37.766 --> 34:39.726
<font color="yellow">Clothes - for Ed.</font>

34:41.606 --> 34:43.005
<font color="yellow">Is he staying with you?</font>

34:43.005 --> 34:45.045
<font color="cyan">He's on the boat, I think.</font>

34:45.045 --> 34:46.646
<font color="cyan">Anyway, how are you doing?</font>

34:46.646 --> 34:48.005
<font color="yellow">Oh, how would you be doing</font>

34:48.005 --> 34:50.246
<font color="yellow">if you discovered the person</font>
<font color="yellow">you thought you knew...?</font>

34:50.246 --> 34:51.686
<font color="cyan">I know, I know.</font>

34:51.686 --> 34:53.485
<font color="cyan">I wish I could help more.</font>

34:53.485 --> 34:55.806
<font color="cyan">I tried to talk to him,</font>
<font color="cyan">but with everything that's...</font>

34:57.646 --> 34:59.366
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

34:59.366 --> 35:00.686
<font color="cyan">He's being questioned.</font>

35:00.686 --> 35:02.046
<font color="yellow">By the police?!</font>

35:03.606 --> 35:06.806
<font color="cyan">When Ed got left that photo,</font>
<font color="cyan">there was something else.</font>

35:06.806 --> 35:10.206
<font color="cyan">We tried to clean it off.</font>
<font color="cyan">I took the photo, just in case.</font>

35:10.206 --> 35:12.246
<font color="yellow">And you didn't think to tell me?</font>

35:12.246 --> 35:13.726
<font color="cyan">Sorry.</font>

35:13.726 --> 35:15.686
<font color="cyan">There's more.</font>

35:15.686 --> 35:18.446
<font color="cyan">I found some tarpaulin on the boat.</font>

35:18.446 --> 35:19.686
<font color="cyan">I thought it had paint on it...</font>

35:20.966 --> 35:22.326
<font color="cyan">..but I think it's blood.</font>

35:23.966 --> 35:25.406
<font color="yellow">George...</font>

35:26.926 --> 35:28.766
<font color="white">SHE SIGHS</font>
<font color="cyan">Hey...</font>

35:32.926 --> 35:34.806
<font color="lime">Open wide, Mr Collier.</font>

35:45.846 --> 35:47.806
<font color="yellow">This was four days ago.</font>

35:53.566 --> 35:54.966
<font color="white">Yeah...</font>

35:59.686 --> 36:02.086
<font color="white">I... Now, you see...</font>

36:02.086 --> 36:04.926
<font color="white">George, he offered to help me, uh,</font>

36:04.926 --> 36:07.646
<font color="white">with my daughter's new boyfriend.</font>

36:07.646 --> 36:08.806
<font color="yellow">Help you...?</font>

36:08.806 --> 36:10.406
<font color="white">Just, um...</font>

36:10.406 --> 36:12.846
<font color="white">find stuff out about him.</font>
<font color="white">That's all.</font>

36:12.846 --> 36:15.646
<font color="yellow">Are you saying that Mr Fitzgerald</font>
<font color="yellow">was spying on your behalf?</font>

36:15.646 --> 36:18.606
<font color="white">No, no, no. Not like that.</font>
<font color="white">Not spying.</font>

36:18.606 --> 36:19.766
<font color="white">Just...</font>

36:19.766 --> 36:24.926
<font color="white">Just finding stuff out</font>
<font color="white">on his... on his computer.</font>

36:24.926 --> 36:27.846
<font color="white">You see, George, he told me stuff</font>
<font color="white">that made me think</font>

36:27.846 --> 36:30.886
<font color="white">that Abbie's boyfriend</font>
<font color="white">was up to no good,</font>

36:30.886 --> 36:35.326
<font color="white">and I made</font>
<font color="white">a complete idiot of myself.</font>

36:35.326 --> 36:36.366
<font color="white">So...</font>

36:36.366 --> 36:40.606
<font color="white">I'm just telling him there to stop,</font>
<font color="white">you know, I'd had enough of it.</font>

36:41.686 --> 36:43.966
<font color="yellow">And George Fitzgerald,</font>
<font color="yellow">by the looks of it.</font>

36:47.566 --> 36:50.686
<font color="white">I had nothing to do</font>
<font color="white">with what happened to George.</font>

36:50.686 --> 36:53.446
<font color="yellow">I'll be the judge of that,</font>
<font color="yellow">Mr Collier.</font>

36:54.486 --> 36:58.046
<font color="yellow">We'll be making further enquiries</font>
<font color="yellow">into Mr Fitzgerald's murder,</font>

36:58.046 --> 36:59.726
<font color="yellow">and I think it's extremely likely</font>

36:59.726 --> 37:02.166
<font color="yellow">that you and I</font>
<font color="yellow">will be talking again.</font>

37:05.526 --> 37:07.526
<font color="yellow">He's free to leave - for now.</font>

37:14.006 --> 37:15.686
<font color="white">What?</font>

37:15.686 --> 37:17.086
<font color="cyan">Nothing.</font>

37:24.206 --> 37:25.246
<font color="cyan">You...</font>

37:26.926 --> 37:28.366
<font color="cyan">You spoke to Claire yet?</font>

37:29.606 --> 37:32.646
<font color="white">She's not interested</font>
<font color="white">in talking to me. Not now.</font>

37:32.646 --> 37:34.366
<font color="white">Not after everything I've done.</font>

37:36.326 --> 37:37.966
<font color="cyan">I've never seen her so angry.</font>

37:37.966 --> 37:40.166
<font color="white">What did you say to her?</font>
<font color="cyan">The truth.</font>

37:41.446 --> 37:43.006
<font color="cyan">You told me you couldn't get a loan.</font>

37:43.006 --> 37:44.926
<font color="cyan">You borrowed money</font>
<font color="cyan">off Phyllis's house -</font>

37:44.926 --> 37:46.126
<font color="cyan">where the fuck has that gone?</font>

37:46.126 --> 37:47.766
<font color="white">I hired a private detective, OK?</font>

37:47.766 --> 37:49.966
<font color="white">I just want to know who it is</font>
<font color="white">who's wrecking my life.</font>

37:49.966 --> 37:51.006
<font color="cyan">Who is it, then?</font>

37:53.606 --> 37:56.046
<font color="cyan">This is about the four of you</font>
<font color="cyan">in that bloody photo, isn't it?</font>

37:58.166 --> 37:59.726
<font color="cyan">What are you so guilty about, eh?</font>

38:01.126 --> 38:02.606
<font color="white">I can't fucking tell you.</font>

38:02.606 --> 38:03.806
<font color="cyan">Well, tell Claire.</font>

38:03.806 --> 38:04.926
<font color="white">I can't.</font>

38:04.926 --> 38:06.126
<font color="white">It'd destroy her.</font>

38:06.126 --> 38:09.086
<font color="cyan">Oh, she's already been destroyed</font>
<font color="cyan">by you lying to her.</font>

38:09.086 --> 38:11.726
<font color="cyan">If you can be honest with her,</font>
<font color="cyan">you can save your marriage -</font>

38:11.726 --> 38:13.606
<font color="cyan">isn't that what you want?</font>
<font color="white">ED SIGHS</font>

38:13.606 --> 38:16.206
<font color="cyan">I've seen all this before, Ed -</font>
<font color="cyan">when Josh died.</font>

38:16.206 --> 38:18.166
<font color="cyan">You nearly lost her then.</font>

38:18.166 --> 38:19.886
<font color="cyan">She was this close to leaving you.</font>

38:21.046 --> 38:22.126
<font color="white">That was you.</font>

38:23.446 --> 38:25.926
<font color="white">When Josh died,</font>
<font color="white">Claire and I, we had counselling,</font>

38:25.926 --> 38:28.286
<font color="white">and she spoke about someone</font>
<font color="white">who she could speak to,</font>

38:28.286 --> 38:30.166
<font color="white">someone who REALLY cared about her.</font>

38:31.366 --> 38:34.966
<font color="cyan">Yeah, well, someone had to,</font>
<font color="cyan">cos you weren't here, were you?</font>

38:34.966 --> 38:36.766
<font color="white">KNOCKING</font>

38:41.086 --> 38:44.446
<font color="yellow">Yes? </font><font color="cyan">We have a warrant</font>
<font color="cyan">to search this house.</font>

38:44.446 --> 38:45.766
<font color="yellow">What is this?</font>

38:47.446 --> 38:49.366
<font color="cyan">Excuse me.</font>
<font color="yellow">Go ahead.</font>

38:50.966 --> 38:54.286
<font color="cyan">Let's start downstairs</font>
<font color="cyan">and work through. </font><font color="lime">Yes, Ma'am.</font>

39:10.726 --> 39:11.926
<font color="lime">Find.</font>

39:17.886 --> 39:19.406
<font color="yellow">I trusted you!</font>

39:19.406 --> 39:20.686
<font color="cyan">I helped her, that was all.</font>

39:20.686 --> 39:22.126
<font color="yellow">My son, he wasn't cold</font>
<font color="yellow">in the ground</font>

39:22.126 --> 39:24.686
<font color="yellow">before you were shagging my wife!</font>
<font color="cyan">That's not what happened!</font>

39:24.686 --> 39:26.966
<font color="cyan">Ah!</font>

39:26.966 --> 39:29.646
<font color="cyan">Ah!</font>
<font color="yellow">It's always been you, hasn't it?</font>

39:29.646 --> 39:30.726
<font color="yellow">The photo,</font>

39:30.726 --> 39:33.326
<font color="yellow">the paint, winding me up.</font>
<font color="cyan">You're talking bollocks!</font>

39:33.326 --> 39:35.086
<font color="yellow">Blaming George,</font>
<font color="yellow">getting me to go after him</font>

39:35.086 --> 39:37.406
<font color="yellow">to get me out of the way</font>
<font color="yellow">so you could shack up with Claire!</font>

39:38.326 --> 39:40.886
<font color="cyan">You've finally lost it!</font>

39:44.446 --> 39:46.246
<font color="cyan">Christ, Ed, I'm sorry.</font>

39:46.246 --> 39:48.406
<font color="yellow">Don't you fucking touch it!</font>

39:49.926 --> 39:51.086
<font color="yellow">Ed.</font>

39:51.086 --> 39:53.006
<font color="white">PHONE RINGS</font>

39:58.846 --> 40:00.166
<font color="white">What is it?</font>

40:00.166 --> 40:02.806
<font color="white">CLAIRE: </font><font color="yellow">'What the hell</font>
<font color="yellow">have you done?</font>

40:02.806 --> 40:05.566
<font color="yellow">'They found your gutting knife</font>
<font color="yellow">in the bin.'</font>

40:13.126 --> 40:14.486
<font color="cyan">Ed!</font>

40:16.966 --> 40:18.686
<font color="cyan">Ed!</font>

40:25.126 --> 40:26.206
<font color="cyan">Ryan?</font>

40:32.086 --> 40:33.486
<font color="cyan">Ryan?</font>

40:39.246 --> 40:40.286
<font color="cyan">What's going on?</font>

40:42.406 --> 40:44.886
<font color="yellow">Not the best timing...</font>

40:44.886 --> 40:47.126
<font color="yellow">but I love you,</font>

40:47.126 --> 40:48.966
<font color="yellow">and I'll always be here for you.</font>

40:53.886 --> 40:55.126
<font color="yellow">Abbie Collier...</font>

40:56.886 --> 40:58.006
<font color="yellow">..will you marry me?</font>

41:14.126 --> 41:15.446
<font color="lime">Where's my dinner?</font>

41:16.926 --> 41:18.206
<font color="yellow">Mum.</font>

41:18.206 --> 41:19.766
<font color="lime">I'm starving.</font>

41:19.766 --> 41:22.166
<font color="yellow">I just need you to talk to me, Mum.</font>

41:22.166 --> 41:23.966
<font color="lime">And I know what</font>
<font color="lime">you're trying to do with me.</font>

41:23.966 --> 41:25.566
<font color="lime">You're trying to get rid of me.</font>

41:27.006 --> 41:29.366
<font color="yellow">I don't know what I'm doing, Mum.</font>

41:31.646 --> 41:33.606
<font color="lime">I love you.</font>

41:33.606 --> 41:35.086
<font color="lime">And I'm only telling you that</font>

41:35.086 --> 41:37.326
<font color="lime">because there might</font>
<font color="lime">come a time when...</font>

41:37.326 --> 41:42.246
<font color="lime">when I may not be able</font>
<font color="lime">to even recognise you.</font>

41:43.566 --> 41:45.846
<font color="lime">But I do love you.</font>

41:47.446 --> 41:49.926
<font color="lime">Oh, come here.</font>
<font color="yellow">I love you, Mum.</font>

41:50.926 --> 41:52.886
<font color="lime">I know, I know, I know.</font>

41:52.886 --> 41:55.046
<font color="lime">I know. I know.</font>

41:55.046 --> 41:58.606
<font color="white">CLAIRE SOBS</font>

43:31.566 --> 43:34.526
<font color="white">CAR ACCELERATES</font>

43:34.526 --> 43:36.246
<font color="white">THUD</font>

43:43.286 --> 43:45.446
<font color="cyan">No!</font>

43:45.446 --> 43:47.326
<font color="white">THUD</font>

44:00.766 --> 44:02.806
<font color="white">HE GURGLES</font>

44:10.046 --> 44:13.086
<font color="cyan">Dad is not capable</font>
<font color="cyan">of killing anyone.</font>

44:13.086 --> 44:14.326
<font color="yellow">Then why is he on the run?</font>

44:14.326 --> 44:16.486
<font color="white">We did something years ago.</font>

44:16.486 --> 44:18.206
<font color="white">I need to tell you the truth.</font>

44:19.246 --> 44:20.726
<font color="white">CRYING: I am guilty.</font>

44:20.726 --> 44:23.086
<font color="yellow">We both know how damaging</font>
<font color="yellow">secrets can be.</font>

44:23.086 --> 44:24.606
<font color="yellow">Abbie!</font>

44:24.606 --> 44:26.806
<font color="yellow">What are you doing down there?</font>
<font color="cyan">Just clearing my head.</font>

44:28.086 --> 44:30.246
<font color="white">I'm challenging you now.</font>

44:30.246 --> 44:31.886
<font color="white">Come on - just you and me.</font>

44:31.886 --> 44:33.206
<font color="yellow">Where are you, Ed?</font>
